originalText.text: I was a patient of Dr. Seiden for 9 years before she retired from her PA practice. I can not say enough good words about her. She is an excellent doctor, who is very caring and loyal to her patients. I miss having her as a doctor and would be her patient at her NY office if I lived a little bit closer!

originalText.text: One of the best doctors I have ever had. I am no longer a patient because she left her PA practice but I was a patient for many years. I saw her through 3 pregnancies and she went above and beyond for me and her other patients. She battled my insurance company for me, went to court for another patient to help her get her children back, she really cares about her patients and listens. She is one of a kind.

originalText.text: In the complex world's we live in, the ability to connect through understanding has become a rare gift. Dr. Leslie Seiden is truly a gifted doctor matched with unparalled experience in the field of psychiatry, fueled by her desire to help people.
